Description:
Ellia Anti Hair Loss Shampoo with olive leaf and herbs is Specially formulated as an effective anti-hair loss treatment and as a true bath of soothing freshness. Gently cleanses and soothes upon the first application thanks to the peppermint essential oil. Rich in olive leaf,thyme, bioecolia extracts &amp; Lupin protein it improves blood circulation, it reduces irritation and itching to bring softness and suppleness to the scalp. As a result, it makes hair stronger and more resistant and prevents hair loss. Hair is left soft, shiny and easy to manage. Scalp is instantly experiences a lasting Non irritability.

<b>250ml Bottle</b>

&nbsp;

A Natural Body cream with olive oil and beeswax.A  richly nourishing formula that gives instantly a silky smooth skin and helps it  retain its moisture for longer.  Our formula is also enriched with vitamin E, glycerin from herbs, propoli and aloe. Its a warming and calming  smell with vanilla,sandalwood &amp; myrrh it has been choosen so to help give rise to passion, sexuality and the touch as a form of communication, to helps us create emotional bonds and the desire to follow our hearts, heal emotional conflicts, over sensitivity, bitterness, hostility, insincerity, and resentment. It gives rise to being unselfish and truly understanding what is required to be in a balanced partnership. <a href="https://www.consciouslifestylemag.com/22-essential-oils-for-chakras/">https://www.consciouslifestylemag.com/22-essential-oils-for-chakras/</a>

100ml jar

&nbsp;

Ellia Hand cream with olive oil and beeswax is a rich in texture nourishing Hand and Nail cream that softens, nourishes, disinfects and restores balance in damaged hands. It is So effective that it can be used by builders! It is as miraculous as a facial cream.

75ml pot

&nbsp;

SOS Balm! A Natural healing balm offering The Most Natural solution for multiple PURPOSES!  An Ultra-rich in texture, balm that restores the skin's barrier function and comfort. Directly targets, redness and irritation by nourishing and restoring dryness and re-balancing the skin flora. Ideal for Ekzemas, psoriasis, Burning s, diaper change,skin with fungus. An olive oil cream Formulated with propolis extract, chamomile oil, turmeric oil, sacha inci oil, beeswax and shea butter: immediate nourishes, softens, soothes, calms and stimulates skin defenses.

60ml Jar

&nbsp;

Αn anti-aging cream with olive oil &amp; herbs. Our 24h Ultimate recovery cream  offers potent ingredients in a light, buttery cream that smells divine! It combines the unique anti-aging properties of everlasting immortelle flower with the boosted effectiveness of saint john's wort flower the enhancement of vitamins f, E and aletocollagen which are  penetrating deep into the skin to help reduce lines and wrinkles. It also contains Agave to tighten and firm skin as soon as you apply and 3 Different weight hyalouronic acid  to pump long-lasting hydration into the deepest layers of the skin. Incredibly gentle to the skin yet powerfully effective, this extraordinary anti-ageing, anti wrinkle cream with olive  provides magnificent day-long moisturizing hydration whilst simultaneously reducing the appearance of facial imperfections. Can be used day<wbr /> or night, face &amp; eyes

60ml Jar

